{"tid":492401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派衝主席台示威引混亂 立法會再度暫停會議","createTime":"2017-12-07T13:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T14:18:32.000Z","uid":84436,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"805e223e9c36f75893a03cb75d0926abb7cdee0c","tid":492401,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1084208/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1084208%2F&d=AfAONR5CkOAEVl4rRvlejARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1cc3b9f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1084208%2F&h=acba51e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1084208/</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會傍晚繼續處理修改《議事規則》的中止待續議案，期間民主派議員突然高舉標語，離座並衝向主席台示威，保安築起人鏈阻止，現場一度混亂，代主席李慧琼其後宣布暫停會議。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨尹兆堅發言時批評立法會主席梁君彥處事不公，「吹黑哨」，民主派其後一同起哄，部分人更離開座位，手持抗議標語衝至主席台前示威，他們又高呼「梁君彥吹黑哨可恥，今日修改議事規則，明日23條立法」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n保安見狀隨即上前阻止，並在主席台前築起人鏈。代主席李慧琼多次命令議員返回座位但不果，她其後稱極度不想引用議事規則去剝奪議員的發言權，遂宣佈暫停會議。"},{"pid":"02f9ff09fbcc53b5ce9fb7a14e8d15e23e396996","tid":492401,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5796f1818a7e474f74d715e6d67bed18a931927f","tid":492401,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a957fd163f25c93a87452f459af525475fa96f75","tid":492401,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"齋睇標題我以為回帶新聞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96dd9b18d5a1b22899a3c1d541e88c5e14e3c717","tid":492401,"uid":71725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"730fa83eba17153d55c7683aff80b22afd537310","tid":492401,"uid":56904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime